10 An Act relating to alcoholic beverages; amending 37A
O.S. 2021, Section 3-111, as amended by Section 7,
11 Chapter 338, O.S.L. 2023 (37A O.S. Supp. 2024,
Section 3-111), which relates to termination of
12 distribution agreements; requiring certain things to
occur before a brewer terminates a distributor;
13 modifying timing requirements; updating actions that
may allow a brewer to immediately terminate a
14 distributor agreement; requiring a new distributor to
purchase any remaining inventory for laid in cost of
15 an old distributor in certain instances; requiring
arbitrators to have certain qualifications; providing
16 for when an appeal of a decision of an arbitrator may
be made; requiring small brewers to purchase any
17 remaining inventory for laid in cost when terminating
a distribution agreement in certain circumstances;
18 providing that a penalty for wrongful termination and
a distribution agreement may include the purchase of
19 any remaining inventory for laid in cost; updating
statutory language; updating statutory reference; and
20 providing an effective date.
